Package photos.structures

Class UserList

java.lang.Object
photos.structures.UserList
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class UserList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
UserList is a serializable class that holds an ArrayList of Users. An instance of this class can be saved and loaded between runs of the application.
Author:
Robert Kulesa, Aaron Kan
